headline: NextEra Energy to meet with investors throughout September and in early October
summary: NextEra Energy, Inc. (NYSE: NEE) today announced that members of the senior management team will participate in various investor meetings throughout September and in early October to discuss, among other things, long-term growth-rate expectations. Investors and other interested parties can access a copy of the most recent presentation materials at www.NextEraEnergy.com/investors.
